reviews.text:
I quite like the meat that they served have not been marinated / flavoured with too much sauce so that we can still taste the freshness of them after grilling. The meats were all well sliced and presented. The environment was neat too. The ox tongue was particularly nice, always my favourite!

No wonder they have quite a number of stores operating, appreciated their effort in maintain the standard of the food and the service.
